      <h2>🔥 Oilfield Breakfast Burrito</h2>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605475122715-990b9c0efb2a" alt="Breakfast Burrito" />
      <p>A protein-packed burrito to kickstart your 12-hour shift.</p>
      <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>2 eggs</li>
        <li>2 sausage links</li>
        <li>1 tortilla</li>
        <li>Shredded cheese & hot sauce</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Instructions:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Cook sausage and eggs together.</li>
        <li>Wrap in tortilla with cheese and hot sauce.</li>
        <li>Wrap in foil — ready for the rig!</li>
      </ol>
