    <section class="recipe">
      <h2>⛽ Rig-Ready Chili</h2>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1601050690597-4b4b4e8c3b7f" alt="Chili" />
      <p>Thick, spicy, and easy to reheat — perfect for cold nights on site.</p>
      <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>1 lb ground beef</li>
        <li>1 can kidney beans</li>
        <li>1 can diced tomatoes</li>
        <li>Chili powder, salt, pepper</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Instructions:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Brown beef, drain fat.</li>
        <li>Add beans, tomatoes, and spices.</li>
        <li>Simmer for 30 minutes.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="recipe">
      <h2>🧰 Lunchbox Fuel Sandwich</h2>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908553721-2072a45df3c0" alt="Sandwich" />
      <p>Quick, customizable sandwich for when the whistle blows.</p>
      <h3>Ingredients:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>2 slices whole-grain bread</li>
        <li>Turkey, ham, or roast beef</li>
        <li>Cheese, mustard, and lettuce</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Instructions:</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>Assemble ingredients into a hearty stack.</li>
        <li>Wrap tight — stays fresh all morning.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

